sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant A as API (NestJS)
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant O as Outbox Publisher
  participant K as Redpanda/Kafka
  participant W as Worker Consumer
  participant I as InboxEvent
  participant L as LedgerEntry

  C->>A: POST /orders/{id}/confirm (Idempotency-Key)
  A->>DB: TX: update Order CREATED->CONFIRMED
  A->>DB: TX: insert OutboxEvent(type=OrderConfirmed, payload)
  A-->>C: 201 CONFIRMED + outboxEventId

  O->>DB: poll OutboxEvent PENDING
  O->>K: produce OrderConfirmed(order.events)
  O->>DB: mark OutboxEvent SENT

  W->>K: consume OrderConfirmed
  W->>DB: upsert InboxEvent(sourceEventId) (dedupe)
  W->>DB: process -> insert LedgerEntry(CREDIT) (unique(orderId,type))
  W->>DB: mark InboxEvent PROCESSED
